WEBVTT

01:47.040 --> 01:48.120
Qing Yi,

01:48.200 --> 01:49.320
you've had good catches lately.

01:50.480 --> 01:52.920
The weather's nice. The fish
have come out to sun themselves.

02:02.520 --> 02:03.400
How come you haven't

02:03.480 --> 02:05.160
been looking for the Star Stone lately?

02:05.240 --> 02:07.000
Ten years, and still nothing.

02:07.080 --> 02:09.000
What's another day or two?

02:11.560 --> 02:12.880
What are you making?

02:13.680 --> 02:15.400
Your birthday present.

02:16.920 --> 02:18.040
How did you know it was my birthday?

02:19.480 --> 02:20.720
You're the clan chief.

02:21.240 --> 02:23.960
These past few days,
all the women in the clan

02:24.560 --> 02:26.800
have been coming to ask me what you like.

02:27.560 --> 02:28.920
It would've been hard not to know.

02:29.440 --> 02:31.080
But this isn't really my birthday.

02:31.160 --> 02:32.560
I know

02:32.640 --> 02:34.480
it's not your actual birthday.

02:35.120 --> 02:38.000
That's why I never celebrated it before.

02:39.120 --> 02:40.800
Then why are you celebrating it this year?

02:44.160 --> 02:45.960
Maybe because we've
been trapped here too long.

02:47.160 --> 02:48.560
As life goes on

02:50.040 --> 02:52.320
day by day in this illusion,

02:53.160 --> 02:55.040
everything's starting to feel

02:55.560 --> 02:57.400
half fake and half real.

02:58.520 --> 03:00.800
Besides, you've been taking
care of me these past ten years.

03:00.880 --> 03:02.720
I want to do something to thank you too.

03:10.360 --> 03:11.520
What do you think?

03:17.200 --> 03:18.280
It looks great.

03:20.120 --> 03:21.320
They say

03:22.640 --> 03:25.320
bracelets made
with langxi grass and shells

03:25.960 --> 03:27.720
are tokens of love
between married flood dragons.

03:28.480 --> 03:30.400
They symbolize a love that lasts forever.

03:31.480 --> 03:33.320
Will you wear it every day from now on?

03:36.960 --> 03:37.960
I will.

03:43.280 --> 03:44.440
Mother!

03:45.960 --> 03:46.800
Mother…

03:46.880 --> 03:48.960
-Watch your step.
-I found something special.

03:52.520 --> 03:53.840
Ten years have passed,

03:53.920 --> 03:55.680
yet you've barely grown.

03:56.720 --> 03:57.760
I don't know why either.

03:58.280 --> 03:59.840
When I was little, my parents always said

03:59.920 --> 04:01.360
I grew more slowly than other demons.

04:01.440 --> 04:02.320
Mother,

04:02.400 --> 04:06.000
this is my birthday gift for Father.

04:10.920 --> 04:12.080
Don't touch it.

04:22.200 --> 04:23.960
Didn't they say touching the Star Stone

04:24.040 --> 04:25.280
would free us from the illusion?

04:26.440 --> 04:28.520
This is only a fragment of it.

04:30.440 --> 04:31.400
Maybe

04:31.920 --> 04:33.320
only the complete Star Stone,

04:33.400 --> 04:35.880
activated with sacred power, will work.

04:37.200 --> 04:39.240
The Star Stone in Wu Zhiqi's hand

04:39.320 --> 04:41.120
did look as if it'd been mended.

04:41.840 --> 04:43.800
But why did the Star Stone shatter?

04:45.440 --> 04:47.440
Where are we supposed
to find the rest of it?

04:52.400 --> 04:53.480
I remember now.

04:54.640 --> 04:56.000
When I was little,

04:56.080 --> 04:57.800
I used to play around here all the time.

04:58.320 --> 04:59.280
By accident,

04:59.360 --> 05:02.160
I dug up this strange little stone.

05:02.240 --> 05:04.960
Back then, I only thought
it looked crystal-clear and pretty,

05:07.040 --> 05:08.960
so I took it home to my parents.

05:09.600 --> 05:11.720
Then how did this fragment

05:12.600 --> 05:14.720
end up in Wu Zhiqi's hands?

05:15.720 --> 05:17.520
Did you ever meet Wu Zhiqi?

05:19.880 --> 05:21.520
Actually, I've lost my memories

05:23.000 --> 05:24.600
of the day my clan was slaughtered.

05:26.040 --> 05:26.920
For some reason,

05:27.720 --> 05:29.040
I fainted that day.

05:33.160 --> 05:34.000
<i>By the time I woke up,</i>

05:34.600 --> 05:37.600
the others in my clan had already
been slaughtered by the Shilin Sect.

05:39.080 --> 05:40.440
<i>I think I saw</i>

05:40.520 --> 05:42.440
<i>Wu Zhiqi that day.</i>

05:44.600 --> 05:46.280
No wonder every time I urged you

05:47.160 --> 05:49.240
to keep looking for the Star Stone,
you always dodged it,

05:49.320 --> 05:53.200
using Shiguang or being busy as an excuse.

05:53.280 --> 05:56.000
In truth, you wanted to stay here

05:56.080 --> 05:58.080
until the slaughter

05:58.720 --> 06:00.440
to see what really happened,

06:01.280 --> 06:02.120
right?

06:06.120 --> 06:07.360
I'm sorry.

06:08.520 --> 06:10.440
Why are you apologizing all of a sudden?

06:10.960 --> 06:12.280
Because I kept stopping you.

06:13.880 --> 06:15.160
You wanted to leave.

06:16.560 --> 06:18.000
I shouldn't have stopped you.

06:20.280 --> 06:22.120
You wanted me to stay
and keep you company,

06:23.520 --> 06:24.600
right?

06:30.880 --> 06:32.440
This illusion is fake,

06:33.280 --> 06:34.920
but the feelings are real.

06:35.600 --> 06:37.120
Are you sure you want to stay

06:37.720 --> 06:39.960
and go through something
that cruel all over again?

06:43.280 --> 06:46.000
To me, not knowing the truth

06:47.320 --> 06:48.640
is the cruelest thing of all.

06:50.120 --> 06:51.400
Then I won't leave either.

06:52.200 --> 06:53.600
I'll stay here with you.

06:54.200 --> 06:55.680
Having someone beside you

06:55.760 --> 06:57.520
will at least make it a little easier.

07:01.280 --> 07:02.200
Thank you.

07:06.400 --> 07:07.320
This time,

07:07.840 --> 07:11.160
I must find out what really happened
at the Blackwater River back then.

07:14.960 --> 07:16.040
Blackwater River?

07:20.200 --> 07:21.040
What is it?

07:23.520 --> 07:25.160
Di Zhu,

07:25.240 --> 07:27.320
I know you like pretty stones.

07:28.000 --> 07:30.040
This is the Radiant Moon.

07:30.120 --> 07:32.200
I plan to give it to you

07:32.280 --> 07:34.840
at the prayer ceremony
before your wedding.

07:42.000 --> 07:43.160
Don't worry.

07:43.800 --> 07:46.320
I know Man Man isn't the killer.

07:46.400 --> 07:48.080
I won't have him burned to death.

07:51.400 --> 07:52.720
That won't do.

08:06.320 --> 08:07.280
Di… Di Zhu,

08:07.360 --> 08:08.680
what are you doing?

08:37.880 --> 08:39.080
I understand everything now.

08:39.679 --> 08:40.559
Too bad

08:41.280 --> 08:42.600
your plan is going to fail.

08:44.560 --> 08:46.320
You've lost all your sacred power.

08:46.840 --> 08:48.360
How are you going to stop me?

08:53.280 --> 08:55.120
<i>Looks like the killer</i>
<i>is hiding in the shadows.</i>

08:55.200 --> 08:56.440
<i>You're in great danger.</i>

08:56.520 --> 08:59.760
<i>I'll undo the sacred power seal</i>
<i>on you just in case.</i>

09:08.000 --> 09:08.920
Lu Wuyi.

09:35.240 --> 09:37.200
Chief Ao, do you know
that Sun is a snake demon?

09:39.200 --> 09:40.920
He came for the Star Stone too.

09:41.000 --> 09:43.800
Fortunately, Di Zhu and I drove him off.

09:46.040 --> 09:49.440
Now all you have to do
is put this hairpin in his room,

09:49.520 --> 09:50.480
and he'll be the killer.

10:11.400 --> 10:12.680
Water…

10:13.720 --> 10:14.760
Water…

10:16.960 --> 10:17.800
Water…

10:18.400 --> 10:20.320
Drop the act. Your father's already gone.

10:24.160 --> 10:25.160
Water.

10:30.640 --> 10:31.680
Water.

10:46.480 --> 10:47.520
Thank you, Man Man.

10:51.040 --> 10:52.680
Thank you, Ji Ling.

10:55.120 --> 10:57.240
It's not every day that I get to see
Master Chi Wen's tender side.

10:57.320 --> 10:59.600
Of course, I had to keep
acting a little longer.

11:00.480 --> 11:01.720
After all, Master Chi Wen

11:02.240 --> 11:05.560
doesn't usually wipe my sweat
with his sleeve.

11:06.080 --> 11:07.760
I can also give you a slap.

11:07.840 --> 11:09.280
It'll have about the same effect.

11:09.360 --> 11:10.200
Want to try it?

11:12.080 --> 11:13.040
What,

11:13.920 --> 11:15.200
are you trying to avenge Ji Ling?

11:18.120 --> 11:19.960
You were possessed by a demon.

11:20.480 --> 11:22.960
How are you still in the mood
to talk nonsense?

11:23.040 --> 11:24.360
You've really got a strong heart.

11:27.080 --> 11:28.920
Master Chi Wen,

11:29.000 --> 11:30.800
didn't you say I had no heart?

11:31.520 --> 11:33.840
Why are you saying
I have a strong heart now?

11:34.920 --> 11:38.320
What do you really think of me?

11:39.360 --> 11:40.400
You…

11:41.160 --> 11:42.640
Calm down.

11:43.160 --> 11:44.760
Once Ao Erlie gets back,

11:44.840 --> 11:47.400
I'll use Word Magic on him,
and we'll know where the Star Stone is.

11:47.480 --> 11:48.720
Why bother catching the demon?

11:49.240 --> 11:50.840
If you don't want to be burned to death,

11:50.920 --> 11:52.000
you'd better run.

11:54.760 --> 11:57.040
The Shilin Sect has countless books.

11:57.120 --> 11:58.120
Haven't you heard this saying?

11:59.360 --> 12:01.240
"Husband and wife
are like birds from the same forest,

12:01.760 --> 12:03.280
but when disaster strikes…"

12:04.200 --> 12:05.320
They fly away together.

12:43.600 --> 12:45.280
No return.

12:51.720 --> 12:53.160
No finding it again.

13:02.480 --> 13:03.760
<i>Let go, Master!</i>

13:05.680 --> 13:06.520
<i>Master Dragon Deity.</i>

13:10.440 --> 13:12.040
I hope you are well.

13:26.280 --> 13:27.400
This demon mark…

13:28.680 --> 13:29.600
It was painted.

13:30.720 --> 13:32.320
I'm not a Green Ape.

13:32.880 --> 13:34.040
Yuan Wuhuo lied to me.

13:51.360 --> 13:52.400
What's wrong?

13:52.960 --> 13:53.800
Pouting again?

13:57.560 --> 13:58.880
After all these years,

13:59.880 --> 14:02.240
are you still blaming me
for forcing you to swallow

14:02.320 --> 14:03.400
the Dragon Marrow?

14:06.760 --> 14:08.760
You actually forced your own brother…

14:09.880 --> 14:11.840
forced me to swallow the Dragon Marrow?

14:12.960 --> 14:14.560
You were blind from childhood,

14:15.160 --> 14:16.720
frail and sickly too.

14:18.120 --> 14:19.240
To grow stronger,

14:19.880 --> 14:20.880
of course, you needed
to take something strong.

14:21.600 --> 14:25.720
I can't possibly follow you around
and protect you forever.

14:25.800 --> 14:27.800
Besides, when I'm not around,

14:28.400 --> 14:30.200
who's supposed to protect
Father and Mother?

14:31.560 --> 14:33.040
When I'm not around,

14:33.560 --> 14:35.440
who's supposed to protect
Father and Mother?

14:36.040 --> 14:37.080
Xizai,

14:37.600 --> 14:40.680
we need a protector in the family.

14:42.680 --> 14:44.800
-Take it!
-Wuhuo! No!

14:44.880 --> 14:46.360
-Swallow it!
-No!

14:46.440 --> 14:47.600
Swallow it!

14:51.080 --> 14:52.440
After you took the Dragon Marrow,

14:53.280 --> 14:55.040
you not only gained sacred power

14:55.120 --> 14:56.480
and got rid of your illness,

14:57.000 --> 14:58.560
but it also healed your eyes

14:58.640 --> 14:59.680
and gave you back your sight.

15:00.440 --> 15:02.360
You should be thanking me.

15:03.200 --> 15:04.720
You made choices for my life

15:05.920 --> 15:08.240
out of your own self-righteousness,

15:08.320 --> 15:10.040
and you expect me to thank you for it?

15:11.160 --> 15:12.440
You're right.

15:15.960 --> 15:17.680
But what's done is done.

15:17.760 --> 15:19.040
There's no point regretting it.

15:20.040 --> 15:23.000
Regret is the most pointless

15:23.080 --> 15:25.160
and yet the most
tormenting feeling in the world.

15:26.560 --> 15:28.240
Look at this chaotic world.

15:29.160 --> 15:30.800
If you want to survive,

15:30.880 --> 15:32.080
you have to be ruthless.

15:32.680 --> 15:33.960
Ruthless to others

15:34.840 --> 15:36.320
and even more ruthless to yourself.

15:36.400 --> 15:37.920
To be ruthless enough,

15:38.440 --> 15:39.520
you first have to learn

15:40.320 --> 15:41.600
how not to regret.

15:46.720 --> 15:48.400
What you need isn't regret.

15:51.400 --> 15:52.920
It's repentance.

16:03.120 --> 16:05.240
You made me swallow the Dragon Marrow,

16:05.320 --> 16:07.800
join the Shilin Sect,
and become a demon hunter.

16:07.880 --> 16:10.760
So why are we disguising ourselves
as Green Ape demons now?

16:13.960 --> 16:16.200
Because we have to steal
the Star Stone before midnight

16:16.280 --> 16:17.320
tomorrow night.

16:17.400 --> 16:19.520
Once it's sent to the battlefield,

16:19.600 --> 16:21.400
there will hardly be another chance.

16:22.400 --> 16:23.560
The Star Stone?

16:27.840 --> 16:29.680
Father and Mother named us Xizai and Wuhuo

16:30.480 --> 16:32.840
in the hope that we'd live
free of disaster and misfortune.

16:32.920 --> 16:35.400
The Star Stone has the power
to destroy heaven and earth.

16:35.480 --> 16:36.480
With it,

16:37.000 --> 16:38.600
we can defeat the demon clans

16:39.760 --> 16:41.600
and end this war once and for all,

16:42.720 --> 16:44.640
making the world truly free
of disaster and misfortune.

16:46.080 --> 16:47.520
<i>A butterfly demon.</i>

16:48.560 --> 16:50.280
He said his name was Yuan Wuhuo.

16:52.480 --> 16:54.240
Wuhuo as in "gaining nothing".

16:55.240 --> 16:56.480
Your name

16:57.640 --> 16:58.600
is Yuan Wuhuo?

17:00.760 --> 17:02.520
Huo as in "misfortune"?

17:06.440 --> 17:07.520
Having silly thoughts again?

17:11.640 --> 17:13.720
The cave where the Star Stone
is hidden is nearby.

17:14.480 --> 17:16.280
Let's go. Put on your mask.

17:16.800 --> 17:18.040
We're going to find Wu Zhiqi.

17:22.119 --> 17:23.040
Something's off.

17:24.200 --> 17:25.560
No return.

17:26.160 --> 17:27.839
No return.

17:29.360 --> 17:31.080
No finding it again.

17:32.120 --> 17:33.360
Your name

17:34.560 --> 17:35.440
is Yuan Wuhuo?

17:37.680 --> 17:39.360
He's not that Yuan Wuhuo,
meaning "free of misfortune".

17:40.000 --> 17:42.080
He's the butterfly demon Yuan Wuhuo,
as in "gaining nothing".

17:48.120 --> 17:50.600
Father, I don't want these marks anymore.

17:52.400 --> 17:53.600
What is it?

17:54.160 --> 17:55.760
Don't you like what I drew?

17:57.200 --> 17:59.120
Your mother's eyes
haven't been good lately.

17:59.200 --> 18:00.800
Make do with these for now.

18:03.280 --> 18:06.520
You both have demon marks.

18:06.600 --> 18:09.120
How come I have to wear
fake ones to fool people?

18:14.000 --> 18:17.720
They all say I don't have demon marks

18:17.800 --> 18:20.280
because I'm not really your child.

18:25.480 --> 18:26.400
Come here.

18:31.720 --> 18:32.880
Shiguang,

18:33.760 --> 18:35.000
listen to me.

18:40.280 --> 18:41.920
You are my child.

18:43.720 --> 18:44.800
You're the one

18:44.880 --> 18:49.200
your mother and I love most in this world.

18:49.280 --> 18:51.640
That will never change.

18:59.720 --> 19:01.480
You're the one your mother and I

19:02.000 --> 19:03.160
love most in this world.

19:04.240 --> 19:06.320
That will never change.

19:11.640 --> 19:12.720
Shiguang,

19:12.800 --> 19:15.400
from now on, if you don't
want to wear demon marks,

19:15.480 --> 19:16.640
we won't paint them.

19:17.360 --> 19:19.200
No, I want them.

19:19.760 --> 19:21.120
Father said

19:21.200 --> 19:23.400
the demon marks are the symbol
of the flood dragon clan.

19:23.480 --> 19:25.120
They stand for courage and strength.

19:25.200 --> 19:27.480
My demon marks are painted
by Mother and Father.

19:27.560 --> 19:29.840
That means you two
are my courage and strength.

19:48.240 --> 19:49.080
Well?

19:49.840 --> 19:51.120
Did you get it out of him?

19:51.200 --> 19:52.520
Where's the Star Stone?

19:53.120 --> 19:54.520
The Word Magic didn't work.

19:55.200 --> 19:58.240
My demon magic
keeps failing me at the crucial moment.

19:59.400 --> 20:01.200
The power of the Formless Moon members

20:01.880 --> 20:03.360
is tied to the moon.

20:04.480 --> 20:07.480
Maybe it's daytime outside right now.

20:08.000 --> 20:10.800
With the moonlight hidden,
it becomes harder for you to use magic.

20:12.960 --> 20:15.040
Now I believe
you're really the Dragon Deity.

20:16.160 --> 20:19.160
That fool Ji Ling
would never know so much.

20:23.120 --> 20:24.480
Aren't you a fox demon?

20:25.440 --> 20:26.600
Why

20:27.320 --> 20:29.640
does your compliment
sound so unflattering?

20:30.680 --> 20:32.400
Ji Ling, that silly boy.

20:33.080 --> 20:35.000
All he'd do was hold out
a handful of raspberries…

20:36.280 --> 20:38.320
I picked these out for you.
They're all sweet.

20:39.040 --> 20:40.800
…and insist I eat them

20:40.880 --> 20:42.120
because they were sweet.

20:48.160 --> 20:49.520
Since Word Magic doesn't work now,

20:50.200 --> 20:52.440
the only way left
is to wait until the wedding day

20:52.520 --> 20:53.840
to get the Star Stone.

20:57.320 --> 20:58.800
Master Chi Wen,

20:59.320 --> 21:00.840
do you really want to marry me?

21:02.840 --> 21:04.840
It's Man Man who wants to marry Di Zhu.

21:07.120 --> 21:08.440
Then tell me,

21:09.680 --> 21:11.400
would Man Man be willing to kiss Di Zhu?

21:19.200 --> 21:22.000
I can find the Star Stone tonight.
Want to make a bet?

21:22.080 --> 21:23.280
What's the wager?

21:24.280 --> 21:25.560
If I win,

21:25.640 --> 21:27.360
you'll give me my favorite thing.

21:28.720 --> 21:29.840
In this snow and ice,

21:29.920 --> 21:31.320
where am I supposed
to pick flowers for you?

21:41.680 --> 21:42.920
I win.

21:47.080 --> 21:48.480
Only Ji Ling would know

21:50.080 --> 21:51.880
that flowers are my favorite,

21:53.200 --> 21:54.440
that I only like flowers.

22:03.600 --> 22:05.320
The day you left the Shilin Sect,

22:08.160 --> 22:09.840
Ji Ling insisted on seeing you off.

22:12.760 --> 22:14.000
I saw him

22:14.080 --> 22:16.280
picking flowers under
the Golden Scale Tree,

22:18.440 --> 22:19.880
so I asked him why.

22:21.920 --> 22:23.040
He said

22:24.320 --> 22:25.480
you liked flowers

22:27.080 --> 22:28.800
and insisted on picking some for you.

22:40.520 --> 22:42.200
There are no flowers here,

22:44.040 --> 22:46.000
-but I can--
-You can kiss me?

22:49.680 --> 22:51.480
I can make some for you myself.

23:00.600 --> 23:01.800
I have an idea!

23:05.160 --> 23:07.920
Why are you making such a fuss?

23:14.640 --> 23:15.480
You scared it.

23:24.960 --> 23:26.240
Everyone,

23:26.920 --> 23:28.400
the prayer ceremony

23:28.480 --> 23:30.800
has always been an Aodeng tradition.

23:30.880 --> 23:33.200
But now, the Radiant Moon

23:33.280 --> 23:34.960
has suddenly gone missing!

23:35.840 --> 23:37.520
-What?
-What happened?

23:38.240 --> 23:39.760
Does this have to do with your plan?

23:41.200 --> 23:42.120
Genius, right?

23:43.000 --> 23:46.000
Chief Ao, such an ill omen

23:46.080 --> 23:47.920
shows that Di Zhu and Man Man

23:48.000 --> 23:48.960
are not a good match at all.

23:49.040 --> 23:52.320
I suggest their wedding be postponed.

23:59.000 --> 24:00.720
If two people love each other,
they're a good match.

24:00.800 --> 24:03.960
How can you deny our love
because of a single stone?

24:06.320 --> 24:07.640
Right, Man Man?

24:12.040 --> 24:13.400
Answer me.

24:14.480 --> 24:15.480
Right.

24:16.560 --> 24:17.920
Right.

24:19.040 --> 24:21.080
-That's right.
-True.

24:21.160 --> 24:22.720
My love for Di Zhu

24:23.240 --> 24:25.440
is like this dazzling Eternal Flower.

24:30.320 --> 24:31.480
It will never fade.

24:39.440 --> 24:40.360
Next time,

24:40.440 --> 24:43.520
I'll make you a flower
that will never wither.

24:43.600 --> 24:44.680
All right?

24:47.200 --> 24:48.680
Take it.

24:51.560 --> 24:54.080
-Good!
-Good!

24:54.160 --> 24:55.080
All right, enough.

24:55.160 --> 24:56.520
Everyone, listen.

24:56.600 --> 24:59.680
The prayer ceremony is only two days away.

24:59.760 --> 25:01.520
Now that the Radiant Moon is gone,

25:01.600 --> 25:04.280
where are we supposed to find
another gem that fine?

25:05.720 --> 25:06.840
Use the Star Stone.

25:07.560 --> 25:09.280
It was meant to be my dowry anyway.

25:09.360 --> 25:12.400
Nothing is more precious
or brings greater blessings than that.

25:13.960 --> 25:15.200
Di Zhu is right.

25:15.720 --> 25:17.840
I'll get the Star Stone now.

25:23.200 --> 25:24.360
So?

25:29.200 --> 25:30.040
Praise me.

25:30.560 --> 25:31.480
Impressive.

25:36.920 --> 25:38.240
So that means

25:38.320 --> 25:41.320
I'll have the Star Stone tonight.

25:44.880 --> 25:46.520
That demon is after the Star Stone.

25:47.200 --> 25:49.000
You and I should join forces first
to capture it,

25:49.080 --> 25:50.400
then deal with the Star Stone.

26:02.480 --> 26:03.480
Chief Cang.

26:04.360 --> 26:07.280
Chief Cang, why do you wear the bracelet
Qing Yi made for you every single day?

26:08.280 --> 26:10.120
A bracelet symbolizes lasting love.

26:10.880 --> 26:12.880
It should be put away properly.

26:12.960 --> 26:14.480
Don't wear it every day.

26:14.560 --> 26:17.120
If it broke, it'd invite bad luck.

26:17.200 --> 26:18.600
It must be Qing Yi's fault.

26:18.680 --> 26:20.680
I told her it should

26:20.760 --> 26:22.640
be put away and kept safe.

26:22.720 --> 26:23.960
That careless girl.

26:24.480 --> 26:25.600
She must've forgotten to tell you.

26:26.200 --> 26:27.160
They say

26:28.200 --> 26:30.880
bracelets made
with langxi grass and shells

26:31.600 --> 26:33.080
are tokens of love
between married flood dragons.

26:33.960 --> 26:35.240
They symbolize a love that lasts forever.

26:36.040 --> 26:37.760
Will you wear it every day from now on?

26:40.360 --> 26:41.560
She did tell me.

26:42.360 --> 26:43.680
I just liked it so much that I decided

26:44.200 --> 26:45.040
to wear it every day.

28:08.840 --> 28:10.080
Another nightmare?

28:19.920 --> 28:20.960
It's all right.

28:21.640 --> 28:22.800
It was just a dream.

28:26.320 --> 28:27.560
Go back to sleep.

28:29.480 --> 28:30.520
If anything comes up, call for me.

28:32.840 --> 28:33.880
Don't go.

28:38.360 --> 28:39.440
What,

28:40.200 --> 28:41.520
are you finally letting
me sleep in the big bed?

28:44.200 --> 28:45.200
Don't go.

30:07.160 --> 30:08.240
Back then,

30:08.840 --> 30:12.000
I thought that since the Star Stone
could cure the plague in Aodeng,

30:13.800 --> 30:15.720
it should also be able to cure

30:16.400 --> 30:18.080
my younger brother of his illness.

30:18.840 --> 30:21.480
So I sent Man Man to steal the Star Stone.

30:22.520 --> 30:23.800
But instead,

30:24.400 --> 30:26.280
it led to the destruction
of the entire Aodeng clan.

30:27.240 --> 30:28.640
So the Star Stone didn't work?

30:32.440 --> 30:33.400
It didn't.

30:34.640 --> 30:37.400
Maybe that was heaven's punishment for me.

30:38.360 --> 30:40.960
Heaven took my little brother too.

30:42.760 --> 30:44.920
A mortal killed him.

30:47.720 --> 30:49.320
How dare you hurt me?

30:49.400 --> 30:50.960
-Look at my hand!
-I left the silver on your stall.

30:51.040 --> 30:51.880
-He is terrible.
-I didn't steal anything!

30:51.960 --> 30:55.760
-What silver? There was no silver at all!
-I really did give it to him!

30:55.840 --> 30:58.440
-He's a thief!
-How dare you steal from me? How dare you?

30:58.520 --> 31:00.680
How dare you?

31:00.760 --> 31:02.960
<i>All he wanted was to buy a clay figurine</i>

31:03.960 --> 31:06.040
as a birthday gift for me.

31:07.440 --> 31:09.040
Who would've thought?

31:10.080 --> 31:12.200
A mortal beating a young demon to death.

31:12.840 --> 31:14.160
Was that the Yuan Clay Incident
that sparked the war

31:14.240 --> 31:15.560
between humans and demons?

31:17.480 --> 31:18.560
That's right.

31:19.440 --> 31:21.240
At the time, people
didn't think much of it.

31:21.840 --> 31:23.480
But Yuan's death

31:24.280 --> 31:27.400
became the spark that lit
the flames of anger and hatred.

31:28.400 --> 31:30.720
Conflicts between humans and demons
broke out across the land,

31:31.320 --> 31:33.920
and in the end,
it led to a century-long war.

31:35.880 --> 31:37.120
Chief Wu,

31:38.400 --> 31:40.280
may I take a look at this clay figurine?

31:56.080 --> 31:57.960
A figurine holding a longevity peach.

32:04.640 --> 32:06.600
Your brother really
put thought into the gift

32:08.000 --> 32:09.280
he picked for you.

32:49.600 --> 32:50.560
Hey there.

32:51.520 --> 32:52.520
What a stupid thief.

32:53.640 --> 32:54.880
Stupid?

32:54.960 --> 32:57.120
Can't you tell my family's poor?

32:57.200 --> 32:59.160
Why did you come to steal from us?

32:59.240 --> 33:02.800
Look. This is the best robe
we have in the house,

33:02.880 --> 33:04.560
yet it's been patched up
hundreds of times.

33:04.640 --> 33:06.640
That robe of yours looks pretty new.

33:06.720 --> 33:08.200
Take it apart,
and I could make two out of it.

33:09.160 --> 33:12.120
Little one, you're quite the schemer.

33:12.200 --> 33:14.800
That's called frugality.

33:14.880 --> 33:16.640
My father taught me that.

33:16.720 --> 33:17.960
Silver-tongued, aren't you?

33:18.040 --> 33:20.400
It's called being articulate.
I got that from my mother.

33:22.600 --> 33:23.880
Wu Zhiqi?

33:28.120 --> 33:29.200
Get inside.

34:23.199 --> 34:25.320
Darling, how do you plan to repay me?

34:25.400 --> 34:26.679
We've been husband and wife
for over 20 years,

34:26.760 --> 34:27.960
and you're still making demands?

34:28.040 --> 34:29.880
Even between husband and wife,
accounts should be kept clear.

34:31.440 --> 34:32.280
Let's hear it, then.

34:33.679 --> 34:35.120
How about this?

34:35.199 --> 34:36.320
Grant me one request
after we're out of here.

34:37.719 --> 34:39.880
-All right.
-No hesitation?

34:39.960 --> 34:41.760
Aren't you worried
I might ask you to rob, kill,

34:41.840 --> 34:43.080
or set fires?

34:44.120 --> 34:45.159
Would you?

34:45.239 --> 34:46.639
No.

34:47.159 --> 34:48.120
But

34:49.400 --> 34:51.560
I might make my husband sell his body.

34:51.639 --> 34:53.560
Cut the flirting in front of me.

34:53.639 --> 34:55.120
Hand over the Star Stone now!

34:55.760 --> 34:57.880
So that's what you came to steal.

34:58.480 --> 34:59.800
I heard the high-rank
Green Ape demon Wu Zhiqi

34:59.880 --> 35:00.920
committed a grave crime

35:01.000 --> 35:03.760
and got imprisoned by the Dragon Deity
in the Blackwater River.

35:03.840 --> 35:05.960
Even chains that thick couldn't hold you?

35:06.040 --> 35:07.520
If you know better,

35:08.600 --> 35:10.840
hand over the Star Stone now, or else…

35:10.920 --> 35:12.800
What do you want the Star Stone for?

35:13.440 --> 35:14.520
That's none of your concern.

36:38.360 --> 36:40.360
Boy,

36:41.120 --> 36:42.760
talk about a hasty retreat.

37:04.640 --> 37:05.560
Master…

37:07.360 --> 37:08.200
Master?

37:15.360 --> 37:17.440
Why did you call me that, sir?

37:18.760 --> 37:20.160
Master,

37:21.080 --> 37:22.200
do you know each other?

37:23.280 --> 37:24.680
We've never met.

37:26.480 --> 37:28.560
Besides, I've long returned
to secular life.

37:29.320 --> 37:30.800
I'm no master anymore.

37:30.880 --> 37:32.000
But I know who you are.

37:35.720 --> 37:37.240
You're

37:38.000 --> 37:39.520
from the Western Regions. You're that…

37:39.600 --> 37:41.080
That demon monk?

37:45.280 --> 37:46.320
That's right.

37:47.080 --> 37:49.320
I'm the demon monk who betrayed the Buddha

37:49.840 --> 37:51.480
and fell into the evil path.

37:52.800 --> 37:54.640
People call me

37:56.920 --> 37:58.080
Xie Lingxi.

38:02.760 --> 38:04.400
Why do you know me?

38:08.440 --> 38:09.480
I just

38:10.920 --> 38:13.040
recognized the Twelve Thoughts
in your hand.

38:15.400 --> 38:17.360
How do you know the Twelve Thoughts?

38:24.520 --> 38:27.120
Thank you, Master, for saving us just now.

38:27.200 --> 38:29.240
Wu Zhiqi, the Green Ape,
will probably come back again.

38:29.320 --> 38:32.920
Please stay and lend us a hand.

38:37.000 --> 38:37.920
I…

38:38.840 --> 38:40.600
I didn't mean to offend you.

38:42.360 --> 38:43.840
I can stay,

38:47.400 --> 38:48.840
on one condition.

38:50.120 --> 38:51.600
Every meal must come with mushrooms,

38:53.880 --> 38:55.120
right?

38:59.200 --> 39:00.200
No problem.
